OL,3,CThe UK's first Ukrainian library opens
OL,4,Cin the South
OL,6,FKateryna Korniinko came to the UK in
OL,7,F2022. She said: "Language is like our
OL,8,Fday and night. When we got this
OL,9,Flibrary it was so important because we
OL,10,Fcan share our thoughts about books and
OL,11,Fwe can support each other and just
OL,12,Ftalk."
OL,14,FThe library, which was officially
OL,15,Fopened by Reading Central MP Matt
OL,16,FRodda, is funded by the charity
OL,17,FReading Studios and is the first of
OL,18,Fits kind in the UK.
