OL,3,CThe UK's first Ukrainian library opens
OL,4,Cin the South
OL,6,FMr Rodda said: "It's providing
OL,7,Fvaluable support to people so they can
OL,8,Fstay in touch with their home country
OL,9,Fand their language.
OL,11,F"People have apparently been
OL,12,Ftravelling up to an hour to come to
OL,13,FReading so that they can read a book
OL,14,Fand talk to people in Ukrainian and
OL,15,Ffeel at home.
OL,17,F"I just think that's so important at a
OL,18,Fdifficult time."
