OL,3,CThe UK's first Ukrainian library opens
OL,4,Cin the South
OL,6,FCurrently the library boasts more than
OL,7,F700 books, ranging from adult science
OL,8,Ffiction to fairy tales for children.
OL,10,FIryna Bakaliar, a refugee and
OL,11,Flibrarian, said: "We're very proud
OL,12,Fthat all these books are purchased in
OL,13,FUkraine.
OL,15,F"They're supporting Ukrainian printing
OL,16,Fhouses and the writers and they are
OL,17,Fpurchased there and shipped to Poland
OL,18,Fand from Poland they are shipped here."
